      <title>孟加拉国估计哈西娜统治期间每年挪用 160 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/bangladesh-estimates-16-billion-siphoned-yearly-in-hasina-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据临时领导人穆罕默德·尤努斯组建的委员会的调查结果，在前总理谢赫·哈西娜执政的 15 年间，每年可能有平均 160 亿美元被非法转移出孟加拉国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/bangladesh-estimates-16-billion-siphoned-yearly-in-hasina-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 11:35:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚占领阿勒颇后派遣军队阻止叛乱分子推进</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-01/syria-sends-in-reinforcements-to-halt-insurgents-from-advancing-after-seizing-aleppo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝鲁特（美联社）——叙利亚军队在一次突然袭击中占领了阿勒颇及其邻近省份的战略要地后，于周日紧急增派部队并袭击了伊德利卜市，试图阻止叛乱分子进一步推进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-01/syria-sends-in-reinforcements-to-halt-insurgents-from-advancing-after-seizing-aleppo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 10:20:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国要求遣返被缅甸扣押的四名渔民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/thailand-seeks-return-of-four-fisherman-detained-by-myanmar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国正在寻求遣返被缅甸扣押的四名泰国公民，据报道，缅甸海军巡逻队向泰国渔船开火并扣押了船员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/thailand-seeks-return-of-four-fisherman-detained-by-myanmar</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 10:05:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
